\\n\\n### Implementation Status: **PARTIALLY VERIFIED** ⚠️\\n\\n**Summary**: The Valkey implementation is **COMPLETE** and **COMPILES**, but tests are **SKIPPED** due to missing test environment. The Redis implementation has **FAILING TESTS** that indicate bugs in the shared test file.\\n\\n---\\n\\n### ✅ Requirements Met\\n\\n| Requirement | Status | Evidence |\\n|-------------|--------|----------|\\n| **Store interface contract** | ✅ PASS | All 8 methods implemented in `store_valkey.go:24-229` |\\n| **Not found semantics** | ✅ PASS | `ErrNotFound` returned via `IsValkeyNil` check (`store_valkey.go:78`) |\\n| **Session key naming** | ✅ PASS | Prefix `\\\"session:\\\"` used (`store_valkey.go:57`) |\\n| **Expiry index** | ✅ PASS | Sorted set `session:expiry` maintained (`store_valkey.go:118-119`) |\\n| **Last-activity index** | ✅ PASS | Sorted set `session:last_activity` maintained (`store_valkey.go:119`) |\\n| **StoreSandbox validation** | ✅ PASS | Validates nil, empty SessionID, zero ExpiresAt (`store_valkey.go:100-108`) |\\n| **UpdateSandbox semantics** | ✅ PASS | Uses SET with XX flag, returns ErrNotFound if not OK (`store_valkey.go:145-151`) |\\n| **Delete cleanup** | ✅ PASS | Pipeline: DEL + ZREM from both sorted sets (`store_valkey.go:159-163`) |\\n| **List tolerance** | ✅ PASS | Skips missing keys with klog.Warning (`store_valkey.go:254-257`) |\\n| **UpdateSessionLastActivity preconditions** | ✅ PASS | Checks EXISTS before ZADD (`store_valkey.go:211-217`) |\\n| **Provider selection** | ✅ PASS | Case-insensitive STORE_TYPE with default \\\"redis\\\" (`singleton.go:19-22`) |\\n| **Valkey env vars** | ✅ PASS | VALKEY_ADDR, VALKEY_PASSWORD, VALKEY_DISABLE_CACHE, VALKEY_FORCE_SINGLE (`store_valkey.go:31-36`) ...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z_logs/AR-018_ST-0.log:\n  Line 5: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775857502315,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286a50ac4ffe4tDrzPYhHoDy9z\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"