ucture and find relevant design documents.\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775857099111,\"end\":1775857099111}}}\n  Line 5: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775857099613,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286ab2b71ffeuhqZhIY2gPBnOZ\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7954e16a001L8GOE8WDbclti4\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7954d57f001ena57dd2MKmKSD\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286ab2b71ffeuhqZhIY2gPBnOZ\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"glob\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-d671b0d35bb34d4d928b49a478b384e0\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"pattern\":\"**/AR-014*\"},\"output\":\"No files found\",\"metadata\":{\"count\":0,\"truncated\":false},\"title\":\"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775857099589,\"end\":1775857099612}}}}\n  Line 11: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775857103357,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286ab2b71ffeuhqZhIY2gPBnOZ\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7954ed3c001bsU8FN52Y4mnaZ\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7954e39e001vklc1ksUmAV4Zs\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286ab2b71ffeuhqZhIY2gPBnOZ\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-609e5ff830de4bb3a4d08b2ef00fcc68\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/store/design.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/store/design.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-014 — Valkey 存储实现 (Valkey Storage Implementation)\\n2: \\n3: ## 模块信息\\n4: \\n5: - **模块**: `pkg/store`\\n6: - **语言**: Go\\n7: - **规模**: S\\n8: - **关联需求**: AR-014\\n9: \\n10: ## 架构概述\\n11: \\n12: ### 设计目标\\n13: \\n14: 为 AgentCube 会话存储提供 Valkey 后端实现，与 Redis 实现共享统一的 Store 接口，支持通过 `STORE_TYPE` 环境变量运行时选择存储后端。\\n15: \\n16: ### 核心组件\\n17: \\n18: ```\\n19: pkg/store/\\n20: ├── store.go              # Store 接口定义和错误类型\\n21: ├── singleton.go          # 单例模式和存储提供者选择\\n22: ├── store_redis.go        # Redis 实现\\n23: └── store_valkey.go       # Valkey 实现（本设计重点）\\n24: ```\\n25: \\n26: ### 架构原则\\n27: \\n28: 1. **接口一致性**: Valkey 实现必须完整遵循 `Store` 接口契约\\n29: 2. **策略模式**: 通过 `STORE_TYPE=valkey` 环境变量激活 Valkey 实现\\n30: 3. **单例访问**: 使用 `sync.Once` 确保存储实例的线程安全初始化\\n31: 4. **错误语义一致性**: 与 Redis 实现保持相同的错误类型和语义\\n32: \\n33: ## 数据结构\\n34: \\n35: ### Store 接口\\n36: \\n37: ```go\\n38: package store\\n39: \\n40: import (\\n41:     \\\"context\\\"\\n42:     \\\"time\\\"\\n43: \\n44:     \\\"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/common/types\\\"\\n45: )\\n46: \\n47: type Store interface {\\n48:     Ping(ctx context.Context) error\\n49:     GetSandboxBySessionID(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) (*types.SandboxInfo, error)\\n50:     StoreSandbox(ctx context.Context, sandboxStore *types.SandboxInfo) error\\n51:     UpdateSandbox(ctx context.Context, sandboxStore *types.SandboxInfo) error\\n52:     DeleteSandboxBySessionID(...\n  Line 21: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775857119309,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286ab2b71ffeuhqZhIY2gPBnOZ\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79552af90018yiFKB1qrFnt6D\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79550fdc0012nbcoqObps9Syz\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286ab2b71ffeuhqZhIY2gPBnOZ\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"glob\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-ed146ec6dd9c4c47b1e324af8b738d32\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"pattern\":\"**/changes/AR-014/**\"},\"output\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-014/delta-spec.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-014/CHANGE.md\",\"metadata\":{\"count\":2,\"truncated\":false},\"title\":\"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775857119287,\"end\":1775857119308}}}}\n  Line 26: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775857123040,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286ab2b71ffeuhqZhIY2gPBnOZ\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79553c01001TjIqFJYlZ4UFGg\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7955308b001qCFLJymubgGVaw\