ALL have expiryIndexKey string field\\n  And it SHALL have lastActivityIndexKey string field\\n\\nScenario: Valkey store uses same key patterns as Redis\\n  Given valkeyStore constants are defined\\n  When the values are checked\\n  Then sessionPrefix SHALL be \\\"session:\\\"\\n  And expiryIndexKey SHALL be \\\"session:expiry\\\"\\n  And lastActivityIndexKey SHALL be \\\"session:last_activity\\\"\\n```\\n\\n---\\n\\n###...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z_logs/AR-014_ST-3.log:\n  Line 4: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775857042651,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286ac03a4ffevNHKrolkCJN1ax\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d795404a1001b08fWOBbUGH0rL\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7953fd4a00113ZrAakAvM2rlm\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286ac03a4ffevNHKrolkCJN1ax\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-af0ef5146b1049b8a2f4e631839a8252\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/.sdd_prompt.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/.sdd_prompt.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: Write design.md with technical implementation details for the agentcube project:\\n2: \\n3: AR: AR-014 — Valkey 存储实现\\n4: Module: pkg/store\\n5: Language: Go\\n6: Size: S\\n7: \\n8: Specs:\\n9: --- deployment/client-go.md ---\\n10: # client-go library\\n11: \\n12: Generated Kubernetes client code for API group **`runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` / `v1alpha1`**, module path **`github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go`**. Source reference: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/client-go/`.\\n13: \\n14: ## Clientset\\n15: \\n16: ### `Interface` (`clientset/versioned/clientset.go`)\\n17: \\n18: ```go\\n19: type Interface interface {\\n20: \\tDiscovery() discovery.DiscoveryInterface\\n21: \\tRuntimeV1alpha1() runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Interface\\n22: }\\n23: 