a Overview\\n\\n新增 Valkey 后端实现，与 Redis 后端并存，用于持久化 sandbox 元数据。支持按 session ID 存储、检索、更新和删除，并提供基于过期时间和最后活动时间的索引查询。Valkey 实现使用 `github.com/valkey-io/valkey-go` 客户端库。\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 新增接口和类型\\n\\n### Requirement: Store interface contract\\n\\n系...\n  Line 20: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775856993611,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286ade9b8ffe345JXsiaQtvma3\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7953452e001ArxWJx0jsqXpvJ\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79531c550010ODAoH7aSTrhMS\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286ade9b8ffe345JXsiaQtvma3\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"edit\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-1f99c61bce5347ddac5ddded116a25dd\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/delta-spec.md\",\"newString\":\"## Valkey 配置\\n\\n### Requirement: Valkey environment and options\\n\\n系统 SHALL 要求 `VALKEY_ADDR`（逗号分隔的地址拆分为 `InitAddress`）。系统 SHALL 要求非空 `VALKEY_PASSWORD`，除非 `VALKEY_PASSWORD_REQUIRED=false`。系统 SHALL 在 `VALKEY_DISABLE_CACHE` 解析为 true 时设置 `DisableCache` 为 true；系统 SHALL 在 `VALKEY_FORCE_SINGLE` 解析为 true 时设置 `ForceSingleClient` 为 true。\\n\\n### Scenario: Single address configuration\\n\\n- **GIVEN** `VALKEY_ADDR=localhost:7379`\\n- **WHEN** `makeValkeyOptions()` 构建选项\\n- **THEN** `InitAddress` 为 `[]string{\\\"localhost:7379\\\"}`\\n\\n### Scenario: Multiple addresses configuration\\n\\n- **GIVEN** `VALKEY_ADDR=node1:7379,node2:7379,node3:7379`\\n- **WHEN** `makeValkeyOptions()` 构建选项\\n- **THEN** `InitAddress` 为 `[]string{\\\"node1:7379\\\", \\\"node2:7379\\\", \\\"node3:7379\\\"}`\\n\\n### Scenario: Password required by default\\n\\n- **GIVEN** `VALKEY_ADDR` 设置且 `VALKEY_PASSWORD` 为空且 `VALKEY_PASSWORD_REQUIRED` 未设置或非 \\\"false\\\"\\n- **WHEN** Valkey 客户端初始化\\n- **THEN** 初始化失败，错误提示需要密码\\n\\n### Scenario: Password optional when disabled\\n\\n- **GIVEN** `VALKEY_ADDR` 设置且 `VALKEY_PASSWORD` 为空且 `VALKEY_PASSWORD_REQUIRED=false`\\n- **WHEN** Valkey 客户端初始化\\n- **THEN** 客户端创建时不使用密码\\n- **AND** `ClientOption.Password` 为空字符串\\n\\n### Scenario: Password provided\\n\\n- **GIVEN** `VALKEY_PASSWORD=secret123`\\n- **WHEN** Valkey 客户端初始化\\n- **THEN** `ClientOption.Password` 为 \\\"secret123\\\"\\n\\n### Scenario: Optional client flags\\n\\n- **GIVEN** `VALKEY_DISABLE_CACHE=true`\\n- **WHEN** Valkey client options 被构建\\n- **THEN** `ClientOption` 上的 `DisableCache` 为 true\\n\\n### Sc...\n  Line 23: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775857022169,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286ade9b8ffe345JXsiaQtvma3\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7953b4af001K2Kd4zlimQ1fR3\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7953458a001NXUFhiFESoej75\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286ade9b8ffe345JXsiaQtvma3\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"edit\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-0a6b6a5fe9aa40688975def9261f8fe7\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/delta-spec.md\",\"newString\":\"## Valkey 实现细节\\n\\n### Requirement: ValkeyStore struct\\n\\nValkey 实现 SHALL 使用 `github.com/valkey-io/valkey-go` 客户端。\\n\\n```go\\ntype valkeyStore struct {\\n    cli                  valkey.Client\\n    sessionPrefix        string\\n    expiryIndexKey       string\\n    lastActivityIndexKey string\\n}\\n```\\n\\n### Scenario: Valkey operations summary\\n\\n| Method | Valkey API |\\n|--------|------------|\\n| `Ping` | `B().Ping()` → string `PONG` |\\n| `GetSandboxBySessionID` | `B().Get().Key(key)` → bytes; `IsValkeyNil` → `ErrNotFound` |\\n| `StoreSandbox` | `DoMulti`: `SETNX`, `ZADD` expiry, `ZADD` last_activity |\\n| `UpdateSandbox` | `SET ... XX`; success requires `ToString() == \\\"OK\\\"` |\\n| `DeleteSandboxBySessionID` | `DoMulti`: `DEL`, `ZREM` expiry, `ZREM` last_activity |\\n| `ListExpiredSandboxes` | `Zrangebyscore` with `Min(\\\"-inf\\\")`, `Max(fmt.Sprintf(\\\"%d\\\", before.Unix()))`, `Limit(0, limit)` |\\n| `ListInactiveSandboxes` | Same on `last_activity` key |\\n| `UpdateSessionLastActivity` | `Exists` key → int64 must be 1; then `Zadd` |\\n| `Close` | `vs.cli.Close()` then return nil |\\n\\n### Scenario: Successful ping\\n\\n- **GIVEN** 一个健康的 Valkey 服务器\\n- **WHEN** 调用 `Ping(ctx)`\\n- **THEN** `B().Ping()` 被执行\\n- **AND** 结果字符串等于 \\\"PONG\\\"\\n- **AND** error 为 nil\\n\\n### Scenario: Ping connection failure\\n\\n- **GIVEN** Valkey 服务器不可达\\n- **WHEN** 调用 `Ping(ctx)`\\n- **THEN** 返回来自 Valkey 客户端的错误\\n\\n### Scenario: Retrieve existing session\\n\\n- **GIVEN** key `session:abc` 存在且包含有效 JSON\\n- **WHEN** 调用 `GetSandboxBySessionID(ctx, \\\"...\n  Line 26: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775857034428,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286ade9b8ffe345JXsiaQtvma3\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7953e496001zOYfjikP4wprIB\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7953b50d001lxowWeZeBepV8r\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286ade9b8ffe345JXsiaQtvma3\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"edit\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-f056832404aa49c0af81967ef07c0082\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/delta-spec.md\",\"newString\":\"## 依赖项\\n\\n### Requirement: Package imports\\n\\n```go\\nimport (\\n    \\\"context\\\"\\n    \\\"time\\\"\\n    \\\"sync\\\"\\n\\n    \\\"github.com/redis/go-redis/v9\\\"\\n    \\\"github.com/valkey-io/valkey-go\\\"\\n    \\\"k8s.io/klog/v2\\\"\\n    \\\"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/common/types\\\"\\n)\\n```\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Redis 和 Valkey 实现的差异\\n\\n| 方面 | Redis | Valkey |\\n|------|-------|--------|\\n| 客户端库 | `github.com/redis/go-redis/v9` | `github.com/valkey-io/valkey-go` |\\n| Ping 方法 | `Ping(ctx)` 通过命令结果返回 `PONG` | `B().Ping()` 返回字符串 |\\n| Get nil 检测 | `redis.Nil` 错误 | 在 bytes 结果上调用 `IsValkeyNil()` |\\n| Pipeline/Multi | `cli.Pipeline()` 或 `TxPipeline()` | `DoMulti()` 执行多个命令 |\\n| SETXX 成功检查 | Boolean 结果 | `ToString() == \\\"OK\\\"` |\\n| ZRANGEBYSCORE | 带有 `RangeBy` 选项的客户端方法 | `Zrangebyscore` 带有 `Min()`, `Max()`, `Limit()` |\\n| 批量 GET | `cli.MGet(keys)` | `Mget(keys)` |\\n| Key 存在性 | `cli.Exists(ctx, key)` | `Exists().Key(key)` |\\n| 地址配置 | 单个 `Addr` 字符串 | `InitAddress` 字符串 slice |\\n| 可选标志 | 无 | `DisableCache`, `ForceSingleClient` |\\n| 连接选项 | `redis.Options` 结构 | `valkey.ClientOption` 结构 |\",\"oldString\":\"## 依赖项\\n\\n### Requirement: Package imports\\n\\n```go\\nimport (\\n    \\\"context\\\"\\n    \\\"time\\\"\\n    \\\"sync\\\"\\n\\n    \\\"github.com/redis/go-redis/v9\\\"\\n    \\\"github.com/valkey-io/valkey-go\\\"\\n    \\\"k8s.io/klog/v2\\\"\\n    \\\"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/common/types\\\"\\n)\\n```\"},\"output\":\"Edit applied successfully.\",\"metadata\":{\"diagnostics\":{},\"diff\":\"Index: /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_202...\n  Line 29: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775857038370,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286ade9b8ffe345JXsiaQtvma3\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7953f25b001WEdJ5v0Xu9bL00\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7953e4ea001BqUdF6rSWddfLV\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286ade9b8ffe345JXsiaQtvma3\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Updated delta-spec.md for AR-014 — Valkey 存储实现 with comprehensive GIVEN/WHEN/THEN scenarios.\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775857038368,\"end\":1775857038368}}}\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z_logs/AR-014_ST-1.log:\n  Line 4: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775856951457,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286ad6f16ffesjUNLGKzJUQsJL\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79529c030016DXraZMom05gDU\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d795291dc001wuFAtVKXworMKh\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286ad6f16ffesjUNLGKzJUQsJL\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_4c6e953ca22d4af69f4a2887\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/.sdd_prompt.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/.sdd_prompt.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: Write proposal.md for the agentcub