_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/.sdd_prompt.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: Write proposal.md for the agentcube project:\\n2: \\n3: AR: AR-014 — Valkey 存储实现\\n4: Module: pkg/store\\n5: Language: Go\\n6: Size: S\\n7: \\n8: Relevant specs:\\n9: --- deployment/client-go.md ---\\n10: # client-go library\\n11: \\n12: Generated Kubernetes client code for API group **`runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` / `v1alpha1`**, module path **`github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go`**. Source reference: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/client-go/`.\\n13: \\n14: ## Clientset\\n15: \\n16: ### `Interface` (`clientset/versioned/clientset.go`)\\n17: \\n18: ```go\\n19: type Interface interface {\\n20: \\tDiscovery() discovery.DiscoveryInterface\\n21: \\tRuntimeV1alpha1() runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Interface\\n22: }\\n23: ```\\n24: \\n25: ### `Clientset` struct\\n26: \\n27: Embeds `*discovery.DiscoveryClient` and holds `runtimeV1alpha1 *runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Client`.\\n28: \\n29: **Constructors**\\n30: \\n31: - `NewForConfig(c *rest.Config) (*Clientset, error)`\\n32: - `NewForConfigAndClient(c *rest.Config, httpClient *http.Client) (*Clientset, error)`\\n33: - `NewForConfigOrDie(c *rest.Config) *Clientset`\\n34: - `New(c rest.Interface) *Clientset`\\n35: \\n36: **Group accessor:** `RuntimeV1alpha1() runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Interface`\\n37: \\n38: ---\\n39: \\n40: ## Typed client — `runtime/v1alpha1`\\n41: \\n42: ### `RuntimeV1alpha1Interface` (`clientset/versioned/typed/runtime...\n  Line 7: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775856871630,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286aef08bffejIuQsuCpsT0NEo\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79512c5f001SmsIDk4y3ONlN8\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79511919001Y0G8RONCAxzVXq\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286aef08bffejIuQsuCpsT0NEo\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I'll create a proposal.md for the Valkey storage implementation AR-014.\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775856871628,\"end\":1775856871628}}}\n  Line 8: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775856871667,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286aef08bffejIuQsuCpsT0NEo\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d795168cf001Qpd1FD5kcptYct\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79511919001Y0G8RONCAxzVXq\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286aef08bffejIuQsuCpsT0NEo\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-ad8965c3169e4abab878cf4f6c7f00ca\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"error\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# Proposal: AR-014 — Valkey 存储实现\\n\\n## Purpose\\n\\n实现 Valkey 作为 session store 的后端存储选项，与现有 Redis 实现并行支持，通过环境变量 `STORE_TYPE` 配置选择。Valkey 是一个与 Redis 协议兼容的高性能键值存储，提供集群模式和更好的可扩展性。\\n\\n本实现扩展 `pkg/store` 包，新增 `valkeyStore` 类型实现 `Store` 接口，保持与现有 Redis 实现相同的语义和功能。\\n\\n## Scope\\n\\n### 模块范围\\n- **包**: `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/store`\\n- **新增文件**: `store_valkey.go`\\n- **修改文件**: `singleton.go` (添加 Valkey 类型初始化逻辑)\\n\\n### 功能范围\\n1. 实现 `Store` 接口的完整方法集\\n   - `Ping(ctx) error` - 连接性检查\\n   - `GetSandboxBySessionID(ctx, sessionID) (*SandboxInfo, error)` - 读取会话数据\\n   - `StoreSandbox(ctx, sandbox) error` - 存储新会话\\n   - `UpdateSandbox(ctx, sandbox) error` - 更新现有会话\\n   - `DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx, sessionID) error` - 删除会话及索引\\n   - `ListExpiredSandboxes(ctx, before, limit) ([]*SandboxInfo, error)` - 列出过期会话\\n   - `ListInactiveSandboxes(ctx, before, limit) ([]*SandboxInfo, error)` - 列出非活跃会话\\n   - `UpdateSessionLastActivity(ctx, sessionID, at) error` - 更新最后活跃时间\\n   - `Close() error` - 关闭连接\\n\\n2. 环境变量配置\\n   - `STORE_TYPE=valkey` - 选择 Valkey 后端\\n   - `VALKEY_ADDR` - 服务器地址（逗号分隔多地址）\\n   - `VALKEY_PASSWORD` - 认证密码\\n   - `VALKEY_PASSWORD_REQUIRED` - 是否要求密码（默认 true）\\n   - `VALKEY_DISABLE_CACHE` - 禁用客户端缓存（可选）\\n   - `VALKEY_FORCE_SINGLE` - 强制单客户端模式（可选）\\n\\n3. 数据结构和索引\\n   - 主键: `session:{id}` 存储 JSON 序列化的 `SandboxInfo`\\n   - 过期索引: `session:expiry` ZSET，score = `ExpiresAt.Unix()`\\n   - 活跃索引: `session:last_activity` ZSET，score = 活跃时间戳\\n\\n### 范围外\\n- 不涉及 `pkg/common/types.SandboxInfo` 结构定义的修改\\n- 不涉及 Kubernetes 客户端代码变更\\n- 不涉及现有 Redis 实现的修改\\n- 不涉及 Valkey 服务器部署和运维\\n\\n## Impact Analysis\\n\\n### 正面影响\\n1. **存储灵活性**: 用户可根据需求选择 Redis 或 Valkey 后端\\n2. **集群支持**...\n  Line 17: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775856910484,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286aef08bffejIuQsuCpsT0NEo\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7952003e001jmzxT5J788N4Gc\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d795194fa00113S4UGusJCMtQ4\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286aef08bffejIuQsuCpsT0NEo\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"edit\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-74cf7154c17d4cfd9c66e0488f947994\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/proposal.md\",\"oldString\":\"- [Redis Best Practices](https://redis.io/docs/manual/patterns/)\\n- [Redis go-redis/v9 Documentation](https://redis.uptrace.dev/)\\n- [Valkey Documentation](https://valkey.io/)\\n- [Valkey Go Client](https://github.com/valkey-io/valkey-go)\\n- [Session Store Design Document](./session-store/design.md)\\n- [Session Store Specification](./session-store/spec.md)\",\"newString\":\"- [Redis Best Practices](https://redis.io/docs/manual/patterns/)\\n- [Redis go-redis/v9 Documentation](https://redis.uptrace.dev/)\\n- [Valkey Documentation](https://valkey.io/)\\n- [Valkey Go Client](https://github.com/valkey-io/valkey-go)\\n- [Session Store Design Document](./session-store/design.md)\\n- [Session Store Specification](./session-store/spec.md)\\n\\n---\\n\\n# AR-014 — Valkey 存储实现\\n\\n## Purpose\\n\\n实现 Valkey 作为 session store 的后端存储选项，与现有 Redis 实现并行支持，通过环境变量 `STORE_TYPE` 配置选择。Valkey 是一个与 Redis 协议兼容的高性能键值存储，提供集群模式和更好的可扩展性。\\n\\n本实现扩展 `pkg/store` 包，新增 `valkeyStore` 类型实现 `Store` 接口，保持与现有 Redis 实现相同的语义和功能。\\n\\n## Scope\\n\\n### 模块范围\\n- **包**: `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/store`\\n- **新增文件**: `store_valkey.go`\\n- **修改文件**: `singleton.go` (添加 Valkey 类型初始化逻辑)\\n\\n### 功能范围\\n1. 实现 `Store` 接口的完整方法集\\n   - `Ping(ctx) error` - 连接性检查\\n   - `GetSandboxBySessionID(ctx, sessionID) (*SandboxInfo, error)` - 读取会话数据\\n   - `StoreSandbox(ctx, sandbox) error` - 存储新会话\\n   - `UpdateSandbox(ctx, sandbox) error` - 更新现有会话\\n   - `DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx, sessionID) error` - 删除会话及索引\\n   - `ListExpiredSandboxes(ctx, before, limit) ([]*SandboxInfo, erro...\n  Line 20: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775856913902,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286aef08bffejIuQsuCpsT0NEo\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79520d4a001XTbDRYNfmv0trP\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d795200d0001HuS80E8PWklrGj\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286aef08bffejIuQsuCpsT0NEo\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Added AR-014 proposal for Valkey storage implementation to proposal.md\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775856913900,\"end\":1775856913900}}}\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z_logs/AR-014_ST-0.log:\n  Line 4: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775856756232,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286b066a1ffeuIkVCINkfD0aS1\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d794fa4b3001Fc48bGgSLkgOxZ\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d794f9a520018GzrmDMWvDh3Xl\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286b066a1ffeuIkVCINkfD0aS1\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I'll help you initialize a new OpenSpec change for AR-014. Let me first explore the project structure to understand how changes are organized.\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775856756230,\"end\":1775856756230}}}\n  Line 35: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775856786025,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286b066a1ffeuIkVCINkfD0aS1\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79501543001bJVGqz3TUqUJzP\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79500935001U5wNfsA0JibXRH\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286b066a1ffeuIkVCINkfD0aS1\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"bash\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-2dae4ea31ff9430abfa0167c826a746f\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"command\":\"ls -la /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/ | grep AR-014\",\"description\":\"Check if AR-014 directory exists\"},\"output\":\"\",\"metadata\":{\"output\":\"\",\"exit\":1,\"description\":\"Check if AR-014 directory exists\",\"truncated\":false},\"title\":\"Check if AR-014 directory exists\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775856785985,\"end\"